    <div class="article-featured-image">
      <img src="/images/articles/balsam-de-buze-natural-si-hidratant.webp" alt="Balsam de buze natural si hidratant" width="900" height="563" loading="eager" />
    </div>

    <div class="article-content">
      <nav class="toc">
        <h2 class="toc-title">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="8" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="3.01" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="12" x2="3.01" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="3.01" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
          Cuprins
        </h2>
        <ol class="toc-list">
          <li><a href="#product-1"><span class="toc-number">1</span>Gerovital H3 Derma+ Balsam de buze reparator cu unt de shea si miere</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-2"><span class="toc-number">2</span>Lavera Balsam de buze Repair & Care (Bio)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-3"><span class="toc-number">3</span>Weleda Everon Balsam de buze</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-4"><span class="toc-number">4</span>Apiterra Balsam de buze cu propolis si miere</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-5"><span class="toc-number">5</span>Melvita Nectar de 3 Mieri Balsam de buze</a></li>
          <li><a href="#comparison"><span class="toc-number">6</span>Balsam de buze natural si hidratant: o comparatie rapida</a></li>
          <li><a href="#guide"><span class="toc-number">7</span>Cum alegi cel mai bun balsam de buze natural si hidratant?</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq"><span class="toc-number">8</span>Intrebari frecvente</a></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <section class="article-intro">
        <p>Daca esti in cautarea unui <strong>balsam de buze natural si hidratant</strong> care sa-ti repare buzele crapate si sa le mentina catifelate, ai nimerit bine. Am testat o gramada de optiuni in ultimii ani, de la branduri cunoscute la mici producatori romani, si am adunat aici ce e mai bun, pe bune.</p>
        <p>Stii cum e, mai ales iarna sau cand bate vantul, buzele se usuca rapid. Si atunci ce faci? Nu vrei sa te dai cu orice, nu? Multe produse din comert sunt pline de chimicale si parabeni, iar pe termen lung pot face mai mult rau decat bine. Un produs natural, insa, hraneste in profunzime si protejeaza, fara ingrediente dubioase.</p>
        <p>Uite care-i treaba: un <strong>balsam de buze natural si hidratant</strong> bun nu doar ca te scapa de disconfort, dar le si repara, lasandu-le moi si pline. Aici gasesti cateva recomandari testate, cu bune si rele, ca sa stii exact ce alegi.</p>
